  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_1' aria-label=\" Putai versus State of Uttar Pradesh pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('1','2025','2025_8_2108_2135','2025INSC1042'); ><font size='4'> <strong>PUTAI<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>STATE OF UTTAR PRADESH </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 8 S.C.R. 2108</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 1042</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010007622025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : VIKRAM NATH<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, SANJAY KAROL, SANDEEP MEHTA</strong><br> Issue for Consideration The accused-appellants were convicted for the offences punishable u/ss.376(2)(g), 201 and 302 of Penal Code, 1860. The High Court dismissed the appeals against conviction preferred by the accused-appellants. Headnotes&dagger; Penal Code, 1860 &ndash; ss.376(2)(g), 201 and that they raped and murdered a minor girl &ndash; Trial Court convicted the accused-appellants for the offences punishable u/ss.376(2)(g), 201 and 302 of Penal Code, 1860 &ndash; Accused no.1 was sentenced rigorous life imprisonment u/s.376(2)(g) of IPC; seven years rigorous<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 26-08-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CRIMINAL APPEAL No. 36/2019</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 3 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('1','2025','2025_8_2108_2135','2025INSC1042','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn bt